{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1682758939.0519562", "card_id": "Q_598097164", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 264}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "五一期间酒店价格猛涨，年轻人玩起「交换旅游」，「你住我家，我睡你床」，如何看待此事？有哪些需要注意的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，有网友发布了一张「2023 年全国各城酒店【五一】价格对比图」，详细列出了今年「五一」期间涨价幅度最大的 30 家酒店。其中最高涨幅 591%，平时 159 元 / 晚涨至 1099 元 / 晚。 面对酒店价格猛涨，在社交媒体上出现了一个新的旅游方式：交换旅行。这意味着两个陌生人互相前往对方所在城市旅游，同时免费居住在对方家中。 「你住我家，我睡你床」，这届年轻人玩起了「交换旅游」，靠谱吗？ | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-5a4d65066c2be60dc99abb552ef0e4e9_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "496 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/598097164"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IuKa+u52giY4eEAMaCDk1MTkwOTE1IJaPqaIGMCE4ngRAAHIJNTk4MDk3MTY0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1682758939.053229", "card_id": "Q_593255596", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 117}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有个基站离我家窗户很近，大约五米左右，请问对人体有没有害？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "就长这样子，不太清楚来问问大家们"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-2385b6c21a74660a6689d7a2bedf5216_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "377 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/593255596"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IuKa+u52giY4eEAMaCDk0MTE2MjQzINqFoaEGMAc4hAJAAXIJNTkzMjU1NTk2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1682758939.0541334", "card_id": "Q_598399800", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "奇迹诞生之地！湖人淘汰灰熊，NBA 历史首次黑八 + 黑七同时上演，你怎么看今年的季后赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "NBA 季后赛今日结束一轮焦点对决，湖人 4-2 淘汰灰熊，上演黑七奇迹。 根据数据统计，这是 NBA 历史首次同时上演黑七与黑八。早些时候，热火淘汰雄鹿，以东部第八的身份强势闯入东部半决赛。 1987 年超音速：首轮 3-1 小牛，次轮 4-2 火箭，西决 0-4 湖人。 1989 年勇士：首轮 3-0 爵士，次轮 1-4 太阳。 1991 年勇士：首轮 3-1 马刺，次轮 1-4 湖人。 1998 年尼克斯：首轮 3-2 热火，次轮 1-4 步行者。 2010 年马刺：首轮 4-2 小牛，次轮 0-4 太阳。 2023 年湖人：首轮 4-2 灰熊。 NBA 黑八历史 >> 1994 年掘金：首轮 3-2 超音速，次轮 3-4 爵士。 1999 年尼克斯：首轮 3-2 热火，总决赛 1-4 马刺。 2007 年勇士：首轮 4-2 小牛，次轮 1-4 爵士。 2011 年灰熊：首轮 4-2 马刺，次轮 3-4 雷霆。 2012 年 76 人：首轮 4-2 公牛，次轮 3-4 凯尔特人。 2023 年热火：首轮 4-1 雄鹿。 NBA 季后赛今日结束一轮焦点对决，湖人 4-2 淘汰灰熊，上演黑七奇迹。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-347e8a336fb8e5695895c95cb60b97f4_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "135 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/598399800"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IuKa+u52giY4eEAMaCDk1MjU4MTI1ILvOsqIGMAE4J0ACcgk1OTgzOTk4MDB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1682758939.055166", "card_id": "Q_459263961", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 96}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你觉得动画《灌篮高手》中颜值最高的角色是哪个？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-fc1665eb5e1fb1862ae563a6a1554bfd_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "121 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/459263961"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IuKa+u52giY4eEAMaCDY0MzM4OTM2IK2j9IQGMAA4gQFAA3IJNDU5MjYzOTYxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1"